The DVP proves reluctant to compromise, but under the combined pressure of ourselves, the President, and our allies, they have agreed to a progressive coalition agreement, one with substantial increases to labor protections. This will be the first government headed by our party, a massive honor for the DDP, and hopefully a sign of better things to come. It will also likely be the most progressive government since the Wirth Cabinets.

- @start_ministries: Continue.

